Workflow:
1) The user will be greeted with a form to fill in the contents of the post as well as upload the image (one or many) and select the main image. @xyz.com/
2) After uploaded the user will have a success or a failure message.
3) If the post was successfully uploaded the user can see the post at xyz.com/display_posts.php
4) The user can edit or delete the existing posts by going to xyz.com/list_posts.php where the posts that have been successfully uploaded will be listed.

Technical details:
1) The website is made with php.
2) Javascript libraries used are: Bootstrap and popper.
3) Database is used for storing all details of the posts. Database used is MySQL.